result.title: A Model Employee
result.description:
To keep her day job at a local restaurant, Neeta, an aspiring DJ, has to wear a tracking wristband. As it tracks her life outside of work, she tries to fool the system, but a new device upgrade means trouble.

The Surveillance Studies Center and the Big Data Surveillance Project present A Screening Surveillance Film. For more information, visit: https://www.screeningsurveillance.com/.

Written by: Tim Maughan
Directed by: Leila Khalilzadeh
